cell.name: MainenCellMod
cell.meta:notes:
Cell based on morphology imported from scripts obtained at http://senselab.med.yale.edu/senselab/modeldb/ShowModel.asp?model=8210.
Note that this represents the morphology as imported from dks577a.hoc, but this structure is further altered in dks577.append.hoc in the original scripts.
The Simulation Configuration using this cell has the extra hoc code from those script files added when generated in neuroConstruct. See Export network -> NEURON -> Extra hoc code.
The original mod files for the Na and K channels are reused too.
NOTE: channel densities here reflect the usage of pS/um2 as units for conductance densities in the original Na and K mod files!!
This cell is not valid due to the adjustments needed above. Not also it cannot be run on GENESIS as it uses the original mod files in the channels
